title: 6 Bedroom 3 Bathroom student housing
posting_body: ['A must see 6 bedroom 3 bath', '**House is within walking distance to both Cub and Target.', 'Easy access to 94, Hamline and Concordia.', '**', 'Great option for college students or fresh graduates.', 'Beautiful home with newly renovated kitchen and lots of living space.', 'Upper Floor: Upper floor contains four good sized bedrooms with a full bath.', 'Bathroom has a large shower/tub and lots of storage.', 'Main level: Main level has large dining room, large living area, kitchen and a (full bath/ laundry coming September 2022).', 'As well as a beautiful three season porch.', 'Basement Level: (Basement has two large bedrooms with full bath/laundry coming September 2022 and also a kitchenette with microwave and fridge/freezer).', 'An extra storage room is available in the basement.', 'This house has a beautiful partially fenced-in backyard with a firepit and gardening opportunities.', 'House has lots of room for off-street parking.', 'Approximately four stalls for off-street parking as well as two garage stalls.', '*House can come pre-furnished for the same price*', '(Couches, recliners, tv stand, dining table)', 'House has in-unit laundry in the basement and is soon to be on the main floor.', 'AC is available.', 'Schedule a time to check out this great opportunity.', 'Security Deposit: $3,500', 'Contact by phone:', 'show contact info']
